Φ(Goal_Setting) = λ(goal|specific-challenging) ∘ μ(commitment|structure) ∘ σ(feedback|distinction) ∘ ρ(self-efficacy|resonance) → [β(performance)] → [✶(satisfaction)] + ε | :motivational

